detail.effect:
[Blocker] (After an opponent's attack, you may switch this card to Rest Mode and change the target of the attack to this card.)
[End of Your Turn] If you have 2 or more cards that include 《Demon Realm》 or 《Demon World》 in their special traits in your Battle Area, switch this card in a Battle Area to Active Mode.
